---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Pulse Academy">
    <main class="min-h-screen py-20 px-4 md:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#050507] to-[#0a0a15]">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
                <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
                <p class="text-gray-400">Last updated: January 2025</p>
            </div>

            <div class="card-gradient p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl border border-gray-800/20 space-y-8">
                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        By accessing and using Pulse Academy's services, including our website, courses, and consultations, you accept and agree to be bound by the terms and provision of this agreement. These Terms of Service govern your use of all services provided by Pulse Academy.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">2. Services Description</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Pulse Academy provides music production education, mixing and mastering consultations, track analysis services, and related educational content. Our services include but are not limited to:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>Online music production courses and programs</li>
                        <li>One-on-one mixing and mastering consultations</li>
                        <li>Track analysis and feedback sessions</li>
                        <li>Educational content and resources</li>
                        <li>Community access and support</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        When using our services, you agree to:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>Provide accurate and truthful information</li>
                        <li>Respect intellectual property rights</li>
                        <li>Not share course materials or content without permission</li>
                        <li>Maintain confidentiality of any proprietary techniques shared</li>
                        <li>Use services for educational purposes only</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">4. Payment and Refunds</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        Payment terms and refund policies:
                    </p>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-300 space-y-2 ml-4">
                        <li>All payments are processed securely through our payment providers</li>
                        <li>Free consultation sessions are provided as described on our website</li>
                        <li>Paid services are non-refundable unless specified otherwise</li>
                        <li>We reserve the right to modify pricing with notice</li>
                    </ul>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">5. Intellectual Property</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        All course materials, methods, techniques, and content provided by Pulse Academy are proprietary and protected by intellectual property laws. Users are granted a personal, non-transferable license to use these materials for educational purposes only. Redistribution, sharing, or commercial use of our content is strictly prohibited.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">6. Privacy and Data Protection</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Your privacy is important to us. Please review our Privacy Policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information. By using our services, you consent to the collection and use of information as outlined in our Privacy Policy.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">7. Limitation of Liability</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        Pulse Academy provides educational services and cannot guarantee specific outcomes or results. While we strive to provide high-quality education and guidance, individual results may vary. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our services.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        We reserve the right to terminate or suspend access to our services at any time for violations of these terms or for any other reason deemed necessary. Users may also terminate their account at any time by contacting us.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">9. Changes to Terms</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        We reserve the right to modify these Terms of Service at any time. Changes will be posted on this page with an updated "Last modified" date. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section>
                    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">10. Contact Information</h2>
                    <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed">
                        If you have questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us through our website or social media channels.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>

            <div class="text-center mt-12">
                <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-pulse-gradient text-white rounded-lg hover:from-[#7c3aed] hover:to-[#06b6d4] transition-all shadow-glow-sm">
                    <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path>
                    </svg>
                    Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</Layout> 